{"tid":1672063,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2019年手11月10日香港大農場有乜野嘉年華會呀？","createTime":"2019-10-24T01:29:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T01:48:15.000Z","uid":270390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5d858d68e2a33253d61296329a54c70e7b851d3e","tid":1672063,"uid":270390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T01:29:02.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟係做香港大農場兼職農場耙泥助理，尋日組長派更有個咁嘅節目<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2koXZBR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2koXZBR.jpg&h=27d6579f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我打電話去大農場d大佬，問係乜野嘉年華會，係邊個機構搞嘅，佢就講到吞吞吐吐，話係乜野愛香港嘅活動，我再問白d，係藍定黃，佢就話係藍藍地嘅。<br />\n<br />\n奇怪在響大農場官方網址，11月份嘅活動名單，亦冇呢個活動，唔知係咪臨時加插。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lnwq8w7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLnwq8w7.jpg&h=c577d716&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n請問有冇巴打知詳情呢?<br />\n<br />\n如果係藍嘅話，我唔撚賺佢d錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，放假拿錢嚴懲黃店好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3a6834172c7d0d47046ce9a6e779449d0ad8705","tid":1672063,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T01:37:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1yYtmny.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1yYtmny.gif&h=db5af89f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f4d34144f1593fad8a8f0ed7dff92a18e85b1e0e","tid":1672063,"uid":81726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T01:45:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"466e16b35436a47aff5ea57611912102d2f421e9","tid":1672063,"uid":270390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4d34144f1593fad8a8f0ed7dff92a18e85b1e0e","tid":1672063,"uid":81726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T01:45:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"repl